    <!-- =========================
         ARTIST STATEMENT
    ========================= -->
    <div class="cv-section statement-section">

      <h2>Artist Statement</h2>

      <p class="artist-statement">
        Cavan’s practice explores the ambiguity and resonance of daily life,
        focusing on the subtle structures and overlooked moments within everyday environments.

        Working primarily in oil paint, he isolates fragments of the ordinary,
        rendering them with a quiet precision that sits between observation and interpretation.

        The work invites a slower form of looking — one that considers how meaning accumulates
        within familiar spaces, and how the ordinary can hold emotional and narrative weight.
      </p>

    </div>

